name: Unidentified_Jawa_youngling_2
content: A Jawa youngling was stationed on the Galactic Society of Creature Enthusiasts' Youngling Care Space Station. The Jawa once threw around a ball with a fellow Jawa youngling, and later played the drums alongside three other younglings. Sometime later, they played a game with supervising Safari droid M1-RE to find the items in which they had hidden.
